{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "One more minute, if the partisans opened fire not that day, or not that-- that day but half an hour later, I get my bullet, for sure.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "That's an absolute miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I still dream about it nearly every-- every week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I have this dream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Anyhow, next day we arrived to a town very near to the Czech border, near Moravska Ostrava.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And there was a beautiful long train with open coal wagons, open.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "No-- no tops just sides, but nothing on the top.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "[GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Every coal wagon, 100 people in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "They pushed us in like-- like sardines. 100 people, 100 people, 100 in here, 100 in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "There was no question about food, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Snow, you could eat the snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And then the train started to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "It went through Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "It went through, from Moravska Ostrava, right through across all of Czechoslovakia into Austria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And that journey, well, I was only half conscious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Because I was better off than some of my friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Because they-- they just went-- they went crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Some of them talked incoherently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Some of them were just crying, mother, mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Some of them just died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Other people, who sat down for one minute, were-- were trampled to death right away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Because if one sits down, and 100 people are pressing, not that you want to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "But the others are pressing you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "You had to step on him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Later on, it got easier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Because by that time, 15, 20 people were lying dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "Later on, half of the cabin was dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "So then we had more-- we could sit on-- put together three dead bodies, and we could sit on them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "But then first, you had to survive the first half a day, first 10 hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "This was crucial.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
